76
00:01:58,150 --> 00:01:58,840
Line photography?

77
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,500
[Kagura]

78
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:00,440
What is that?

79
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:04,740
