87
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:23,250
[Photography]

88
00:02:13,880 --> 00:02:15,380
[Gintoki]

89
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,700
Hey, there's color in those.

90
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:30,900
[Shinpachi]

91
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:17,080
These are archives.

92
00:02:17,660 --> 00:02:21,000
During this process, there may be times when they have to do

93
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,270
