94
00:02:23,250 --> 00:02:28,260
[Line photography]

95
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:26,410
They have no choice but to photograph the line drawings from the original pictures.

96
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:27,930
This is what we call line photography.

97
00:02:28,810 --> 00:02:30,830
The voice actors who do voice-overs are familiar with this, right?

98
00:02:31,130 --> 00:02:34,770
[Gintoki]

99
