101
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,270
[Kagura]

102
00:02:35,150 --> 00:02:37,370
So you're telling me it'll be all white till the end?

103
00:02:37,640 --> 00:02:45,410
[Shinpachi]

104
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:41,440
